snippet.title: Jujutsu Kaisen Cursed Clash – Character Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Master a new domain and catch the intense combat between Yuji Itadori, Megumi Fushiguro, Nobara Kugisaki, Satoru Gojo, and Ryomen Sukuna! 

Jujutsu Kaisen Cursed Clash is coming to PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, PC, and Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch.
#JujutsuKaisen #JJK
